{"tid":809760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"炸彈染血書包相洗版　軍火商爆公關災難急刪貼文","createTime":"2018-09-07T12:09:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T01:53:38.000Z","uid":28765,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9003c9f6a095da317d61a54946c4ef5766343e","tid":809760,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:09:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180821/photo/bkn-20180821180001876-0821_00972_001_01p.jpg?20180821181326\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20180821%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180821180001876-0821_00972_001_01p.jpg%3F20180821181326&h=20496321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民上載也門遍地染血學童書包的照片。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n美國軍火商洛歇馬丁（Lockheed Martin）上周三（15日）於社交網Twitter發文，邀請網民上載公司產品的「精彩相片」。不過，洛歇馬丁卻收到早前炸中也門校巴、由該公司製造的炸彈碎片及染血書包照片，引發公關災難。洛歇馬丁事後刪除貼文，但截圖仍在網上瘋傳，更有網民留言斥洛歇馬丁雙手染血。 <br />\n<br />\n洛歇馬丁邀請網民在周日（19日）的世界照片日上載其產品的照片，惟美國有線電視新聞網絡（CNN）披露本月初擊中也門校巴的炸彈，正是由洛歇馬丁生產，網民隨即以當時的炸彈碎片、染血書包等照片洗版，直指該枚重達500磅的MK82型激光制導炸彈，正是由洛歇馬丁生產。部分人留言指︰「雙手沾滿鮮血︰洛歇馬丁！」又有人諷刺稱︰「他們肯定對自家產品的應用很自豪。」 <br />\n<br />\n以沙特阿拉伯為首的聯軍部隊，向也門叛軍青年運動佔據地發動襲擊，炸彈擊中一輛載滿學童的巴士，造成逾40名學童死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180821/photo/bkn-20180821180001876-0821_00972_001_02p.jpg?20180821181326\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20180821%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180821180001876-0821_00972_001_02p.jpg%3F20180821181326&h=7857ca09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n月初炸死多名也門學童的炸彈為洛歇馬丁所製。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180821/mobile/bkn-20180821180001876-0821_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20180821%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180821180001876-0821_00972_001.html&d=EAXJ%2Fs%2BQrGjAWLZqT%2Ff6zL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=95a0e51f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20180821/mobile/bkn-20180821180001876-0821_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n其實佢諗住有咩人同埋有咩產品可以分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1349975472c3def83f2d809c177f14c70f278c9","tid":809760,"uid":155818,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:10:28.000Z","msg":"死左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f1e94204ed1e595ef7972a96480521ff9c1e78e","tid":809760,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6bcbda9060d48581158eb86e8694b16545f654","tid":809760,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0b8ed25ae329f0c44a56810d14a57e4ddcd48f1","tid":809760,"uid":94828,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:18:17.000Z","msg":"真係好大貢獻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1cbc019b3aabc3d3929e538329b53d9603a308d","tid":809760,"uid":20241,"like":18,"dislike":3,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:20:15.000Z","msg":"為地球清除癌細胞係好事<br />\n點解要刪文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf03b64872643f359a85b6a47398dea62c47d427","tid":809760,"uid":89931,"like":26,"dislike":2,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 左膠都幾好笑 唔講仲以為 啲導彈係洛克馬丁射出去嘅"},{"pid":"7ca544df81ecb313093f0846e383490f203f29ce","tid":809760,"uid":25424,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:56:44.000Z","msg":"人地唔係生產炸彈唔通出condom呀？<br />\n<br />\n阿拉伯佬自己互炸關間公司乜事"},{"pid":"943a4e46b76b1148383526ccaece143b71704c50","tid":809760,"uid":121146,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T12:59:55.000Z","msg":"左膠都痴撚線"},{"pi